  <text>
    <front>
      <div type="printedheader">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7765_p1">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <fw>THE MACHINE TUNNELLING COMPANY, LIMITED</fw>
        </p>
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7765_p2">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>
          <fw>2. Westminster Chambers,
            <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>Victoria Street, <choice>
                            <abbr>S.W.</abbr>
                            <expan>SouthWest (Südwesten)</expan>
                        </choice> </fw>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7765_p3">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>
          <fw>
            <placeName type="place" key="London (UK)">London</placeName>
          </fw>
          <date when="1872-05-15">15<hi rend="sup">th</hi> May <fw>187</fw>2</date>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="address">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7765_p4">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>
          <choice>
                        <abbr>Mons<hi rend="sup">r</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>Monsieur (Herr)</expan>
                    </choice> A. Escher<lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>– <supplied>
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>etc.</abbr>
                            <expan>et cetera (und anderes)</expan>
                        </choice> </supplied> – <supplied>
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>etc.</abbr>
                            <expan>et cetera (und anderes)</expan>
                        </choice> </supplied> –</p>
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7765_p5">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>
          <placeName type="place" key="Luzern (Stadt)">Lucerne</placeName>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7765_p6">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>Sir,</p>
      </div>
    </front>
    <body>
            <div>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7765_p7">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>With reference to the advertisement
        <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>of the <date when="1872-04-05">5<hi rend="sup">th</hi> April</date>, calling for Tenders to
        <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>Execute the <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">St. Gothard</placeName> Tunnel. –</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7765_p8">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>The Machine Tunnelling Company
        <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>hereby begs to confirm their offer
        <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>previously made. – <choice>
                        <abbr>viz<hi rend="sup">t</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>videlicet (nämlich)</expan>
                    </choice>: to Construct
        <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>the St. <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gothard</placeName> Tunnel at Ten
        <lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>per Cent under the prices specified
        <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>in the estimate of the technical
        <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>report addressed to the Committee
        <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>of the <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">St. Gothard</placeName> by the Experts,
        <lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>
                <choice>
                        <abbr>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>Monsieur (Herr)</expan>
                    </choice> <persName type="person" key="Beckh August von">A. Becker</persName> of <placeName type="place" key="Stuttgart (D)">Stuttgard</placeName>, and
        <pb n="2"/>
                <lb xml:id="p2-l1"/>
                <choice>
                        <abbr>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>Monsieur (Herr)</expan>
                    </choice> <persName type="person" key="Gerwig Robert">R. Gerwig</persName> of <placeName type="place" key="Karlsruhe (D)">Carlshrue</placeName>
                <note type="transcript">sic!</note>, and to
        <lb xml:id="p2-l2"/>deliver the Tunnel complete after the
        <lb xml:id="p2-l3"/>lapse of 6. years from the date of
        <lb xml:id="p2-l4"/>our fairly commencing work. –
        </p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7765_p9">
                <lb xml:id="p2-l5"/>We will also find any
        <lb xml:id="p2-l6"/>reasonable guarantee for the
        <lb xml:id="p2-l7"/>fulfilment of our engagement
        <lb xml:id="p2-l8"/>that may be requested. –</p>
    </div>
        </body>
    <back>
      <div type="closer">
                <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7765_p10">
                    <lb xml:id="p2-l9"/>I have the honour
        <lb xml:id="p2-l10"/>to be, Sir,
        <lb xml:id="p2-l11"/>Your <choice>
                        <abbr>obed<hi rend="sup">t</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>obedient (ergeben)</expan>
                    </choice> Servant</p> </div>
     <div type="address"> <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7765_p11">
                    <lb xml:id="p2-l12"/>Fred Beaumont.
        <lb xml:id="p2-l13"/>Chairman of the
        <lb xml:id="p2-l14"/>Machine Tunnelling Company
        <lb xml:id="p2-l15"/>Limited</p> </div>
    </back>
